# Environment Configuration
# This file serves as a template for required environment variables.
# Do NOT commit sensitive data to version control.

# Database (Automatically configured by Electron at runtime)
# In packaged applications, the database is stored in the user's application data directory
# DATABASE_URL will be set automatically by the main Electron process

# Node Environment (set automatically)
# NODE_ENV=production (for packaged apps) or development (for dev mode)
